attributes.long-description:
A dark and violent crime thriller, set against the backdrop of 1940’s Los Angeles. L.A. Noire: The Complete Edition includes all previously released DLC. Initial download contains Traffic and Patrol case desks (6.67GB). Arson (3.5GB), Vice (2.8GB) and Homicide (5.2GB) case desks must each be downloaded separately at no charge and will only be playable with the initial download installed.
